 144',NULL,NULL,'Apple-iPhone-13-Pro-Max','Apple-iPhone-13-Pro-Max',160000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(76,'Huawei 40W Supercharge','Huawei 40W Supercharge','Huawei-40W-Supercharge','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,14,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Huawei 40W Supercharge','<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\"><h2>Official Huawei SuperCharge 40W</h2><p>When it comes to charging your Huawei device there is no other product better than the official Huawei 40W Supercharger. Get the Huawei 40W Supercharge for universal compatibility and comprehensive safety protection.</p><h4>Compatible with:</h4><p>P30',NULL,NULL,'Huawei-40W-Supercharge','Huawei-40W-Supercharge',3500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(77,'Huawei Band 6','Huawei Band 6','Huawei-Band-6','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,14,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Huawei Band 6','<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\"><h2>Huawei Band 6</h2><p>The Huawei Band 6 price in Kenya is Ksh 7000. This is one of the feature-rich smart fitness trackers available in Kenya with one of the best sleep tracking algorithms. The Huawei Band 6 is a major update to its predecessor the popular Huawei Band 4.</p><h3 class=\"has-text-align-center tth\"><span class=\"has-inline-color\"><strong>Huawei Band 6 Specs and price</strong></span></h3><figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-regular\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td><strong><span class=\"has-inline-color\">Water-Resistant</span></strong></td><td>Yes',NULL,NULL,'Huawei-Band-6','Huawei-Band-6',6800,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(78,'Huawei Nova 10','Huawei Nova 10','Huawei-Nova-10','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,14,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Huawei Nova 10','<h2 class=\"mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col entity-sec\"><strong>Huawei Nova 10 </strong><strong>Specifications </strong><strong>in Kenya</strong></h2>\r\\n<h3><b>Design.</b></h3>\r\\nHuawei Nova 10 has an exquisite design that is robust, exciting and impressive. This design is ultra-slim, sleek and stylish. The device weighs a mere 168 g and has an ultra-thin thickness of 6.9mm making it light, handy and extremely portable. This wonder of a smartphone comes in two SIM variants; a single SIM(Nano-SIM) and a Dual SIM(Nano-SIM, dual-standby)\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<h3><b>Display.</b></h3>\r\\nThe phone has a 6.67-inch OLED display that is bright, sharp and colorful. This display has 1B colors and HDR10 for an engrossing viewing experience. It has a high-definition 1080 x 2400 pixels resolution and 120 Hz refresh rate. Its screen-to-body ratio is 89.6% with an aspect ratio of 20:9 (395 ppi density) making the display large and wholesome.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<h3><b>Camera.</b></h3>\r\\nHuawei Nova 10 is a great companion for your outdoor excursions. It is equipped with two magnificent cameras for that purpose. The main camera features;\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>50 MP, f/1.9, 27mm (wide), PDAF</li>\r\\n 	<li>8 MP, f/2.2, 112° (ultrawide)</li>\r\\n 	<li>2 MP, f2.4, (depth)</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nThis camera features LED flash, HDR and panorama. Its video capability is equally impressive. You get 4K, 1080p, and 720p@960fps. Huawei Nova 10 takes detailed photos with color, balanced sharpness and a real-life feel. Its videos are High definition with magnificent clarity and beauty. The selfie camera is a single 60 MP, f/2.4, 100° (ultrawide)with HDR. This fantastic camera is a huge selling point of the Huawei Nova 10. You can shoot 4K@30fps and 1080p@30fps HD videos with this camera which is ideal for video conferencing and selfie videos.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<h3><b>Performance.</b></h3>\r\\nHuawei Nova 10 runs on the Qualcomm SM7325 Snapdragon 778G 4G (6 nm) chipset and is powered by an Octa-core (4×2.4 GHz Kyro 670 &amp; 4×1.80 GHz Kyro 670) processor. Topping this with 8GB of RAM gives you speed, power and robustness as you flip through your apps, play games and explore online content. It features the all-new <strong><em>HarmonyOS 2.0</em></strong> but does not support Google Play Services.\r\\n\r\\nThe phone has two memory variants namely; a 128 GB version and a 256 GB version that give you unlimited freedom and space to store your favorite content from music, photos, videos and apps.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<h3><b>Battery Life.</b></h3>\r\\nHuawei Nova 10 comes with a 4000mAh Li-Po battery which is less compared to the previous <em>Huawei Nova 9</em>. This can power your device for a whole day. An exceptional  66W fast charging, similar to that of <em>Nova 8</em>, promises to power you up as fast as you like. Additional power features include reverse charging.\r\\n<h3>Connectivity</h3>\r\\nThe phone has VoLTE with dual standby, Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 5.2, and a v2.0 USB Type-C port. There is also an A-GPS with GPS live-locating.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<h3><b>Available Colors.</b></h3>\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Black</li>\r\\n 	<li>Green</li>\r\\n 	<li>Silver</li>\r\\n 	<li>Violet</li>\r\\n</ul>',NULL,NULL,'Huawei-Nova-10','Huawei-Nova-10',65000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(79,'Huawei Nova Y90','Huawei Nova Y90','Huawei-Nova-Y90','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,14,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Huawei Nova Y90','<h2>Huawei Nova Y90 Specifications in Kenya</h2>\r\\n<span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Huawei Nova Y90 price in Kenya is Ksh 30,000. The Nova Y90 phone features 6.75 inches IPS display with a resolution of</span> 1080 x 2388 <span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">pixels. The phone has a triple-camera setup that consists of 50MP + 2MP+ 2MP and an 8MP camera for selfies. It runs on the Qualcomm Snapdragon 680 4G processor with Adreno 610 GPU. It has 8GB RAM and 128GB storage and runs on EMUI 12. The phone is available in Crystal Blue, Pearl White, Emerald Green, and Midnight Black colors and is powered by a 5000mAh, non-removable.</span>\r\\n<h4>Design and Build</h4>\r\\nHuawei Nova Y90 has an ergonomic design, premium feels, and look. It is made of back glass, front corning gorilla glass, and a plastic frame. The sides and corners are nicely curved, alongside notable thinness in terms of width. The unique camera deck design at the back will get you also ticking to experience the handset fully. The device measures 163.3 x 74.7 x 8.4 mm and weighs 195g.\r\\n\r\\nEnjoy a high-quality display on the large IPS LCD as you play your favorite games, explore the internet or use your handset for work. The device features a large, 6.7-inch display with a refresh rate of 90Hz. The IPS LCD has an impressive 1080 x 2388 pixels (~391 PPI density) resolution.\r\\n<h4>Camera</h4>\r\\nAt the front, Huawei Nova Y90 packs a single 8 MP, f/2.0 with 1080p@30fps video capture capabilities. You can record videos and take decent shots with 0n the camera.\r\\n\r\\nAt the back, Nova Y90 packs a triple camera setup consisting of 50 MP, f/1.8, (wide), PDAF lens + 2 MP, f/2.4, (macro) sensor and 2 MP, f/2.4, (depth) sensors. The main camera asset promises a great show with specifics and AI support. The LED flash, panorama and HDR provide options necessary to enable variety and smart choices when seeking snaps with certain characteristics.\r\\n<h4>Processing Capacity</h4>\r\\nHuawei Nova Y90 does not support Android, offering an alternative experience with the refreshed and new-looking EMUI 12. Huawei runs on its own created OS, EMUI 12. Running background applications and ensuring the device does not lag, overheat or stutter when in use is a powerful and fast Qualcomm SM6225 Snapdragon 680 4G (6 nm) chipset, complemented with an Octa-core (4×2.4 GHz Kryo 265 Gold &amp; 4×1.9 GHz Kryo 265 Silver) CPU and Adreno 610 GPU. The processing unit will not disappoint when it comes to efficiency in performance, fast response, and keeping the device at peak when on display.\r\\n<h4>Internal Storage</h4>\r\\nHuawei packed decent and sufficient internal memory space in their Nova Y90. It comes with inbuilt internal storage and RAM of:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>128GB 4GB RAM</li>\r\\n 	<li>128GB 6GB RAM</li>\r\\n 	<li>128GB 8GB RAM.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nIt does not support MicroSD, which is kind of disappointing.\r\\n<h4>Connectivity</h4>\r\\nHuawei Nova Y90 is 4G-enabled, supporting 4G Bands network connectivity. It has a 3.5mm jack and will support a hands-free, wired headphone connection. It supports Bluetooth pairing, Wifi, NFC, and USB On the Go. However, the Y90 handset does not support FM Radio.The sensors installed on the Nova are the Fingerprint (side-mounted), accelerometer, compass, and Virtual proximity sensing. GPs positioning is supported by the handset (GPS, GLONASS, BDS, GALILEO, QZSS).\r\\n<h4>Battery.</h4>\r\\nThe device is powered by a Li-Po 5000 mAh, non-removable battery. It supports Fast charging 40W, with the capability of charging 0-50% in 30 min.\r\\n<table id=\"tablepress-3023\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3023\" aria-describedby=\"tablepress-3023-description\">\r\\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Model</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Huawei nova Y90</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Announced</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">2022, June 23</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Released</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">2022, June 23</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Operating System</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>EMUI 12, no Google Play Services</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Chipset</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Qualcomm SM6225 Snapdragon 680 4G (6 nm)</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>CPU Speed</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Octa-core (4×2.4 GHz Kryo 265 Gold &amp; 4×1.9 GHz Kryo 265 Silver)</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-8\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>GPU Graphics Processor</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Adreno 610</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-9\">\r\\n<td class