roximity sensor, and fingerprint sensor.',NULL,NULL,'Infinix-Note-30-Pro','Infinix-Note-30-Pro',48000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(91,'Infinix Note 30 VIP','Infinix Note 30 VIP','Infinix-Note-30-VIP','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,6,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Infinix Note 30 VIP','The Infinix Note 30 5G is powered by the Mediatek Dimensity 8050(6 nm) processor with Mali-G57 MC2 GPU all this is powered by a 5,000 mAh battery with 68W All-Round FastCharge. The phone comes with 12 GB RAM and 256GB of internal storage which is expandable using microSDXC and it runs on Android 13. It also has a triple rear camera that consists of a 108 MP primary camera along with a 2MP depth camera, a 2MP sensor, and a 32 MP front-facing camera. The Infinix Note 30 5G is available in colors Magic Black, Glacier White, and Racing Edition.\r\\n<h2>Physical Attributes</h2>\r\\nThe phone is sleek and elegant, with the body made of a glass front, plastic frame, and glass back. The new material and finishing give it a feel of elegance and superiority everywhere. The use of glass is the first on Infinix smartphones, especially for the Note 30 series models. The flash finishing is characterized by streaming light overflowing colors. The bright middle frame is the product of the NCVM process on the flagship handset. It weighs 190g and measures 162.7 x 75.9 x 8.2 mm. It’s a massive handset, and the premium feels once you grasp, it is too good not to experience.\r\\n\r\\nThe phone is dual SIM, giving it versatility and options for you. An IP53 rating makes it ideal to use outdoors as it is water- and dust-proof. A side-mounted fingerprint sensor helps enhance the security of the phone. It comes in Magic Black, Glacier White, and Racing Edition colors to wrap a round-up on the phone. The set of colors is excellent on both the leather and glass back, bringing the best out of the set aesthetics.\r\\n<h2>A Bright, Immersive, Cinematic Display</h2>\r\\nEnjoy a 10-bit HD+ Cinematic and high-quality display on the 6.67-inch AMOLED Display. The 10-bit AMOLED Display flagship-caliber visual experience is like others on the Infinix Note 30 VIP. This 10-bit screen allows for better color reproduction and a more detailed display. The super large AMOLED screen makes the color more realistic and vivid. You will have a great experience watching your favorite series or playing games on the phone. The display boasts of 360Hz sampling rate, 85.6 % screen-to-body ratio and 120Hz refresh rate, 1920 Hz PWM Dimming, 900 nits Peak Brightness and 5000000:1 contrast ratio.\r\\n\r\\nWith the support of Smart Refresh 2.1 and Magellan Engine 1.1, you can get a better experience with a high refresh rate, greatly enriching the experience of many scenes. Whether it’s gaming or watching videos, it’s an unprecedented improvement. The high 1080 x 2460 pixels resolution is immersive and excellent for a great user experience when you browse the Internet or sit down to enjoy a movie series. The high refresh rate at 120 Hz enables seamless scrolling with no lags. Ultra-slim bezel design is impactful to visual perception. The upper and lower bezels are 2.3mm, the left, and right bezels are 1.4mm, and the screen-to-body ratio is 93%. It is still a flagship-level product.\r\\n<h2>Ultra Modern Camera Set-up</h2>\r\\n<h3>Selfie Camera</h3>\r\\nCapture selfies with the decent 32MP lens with Dual flashlight for low light conditions. The 32MP Selfie Camera preserves your beauty. The front-facing flash lets you get clear selfie photos day or night.\r\\n\r\\nUsing the Macro Camera, you can capture the texture of leaves and flower petals to better observe the microscopic world.\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Style Makeup:</strong> Customized makeup for men and women, respectively, instantly improves the tone, an essential switch style, and shows a multi-faceted personality self.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Sky Remap:</strong> This feature can turn a hazy day into a cloudless sunny noon in seconds. Let the sky express emotions.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Dual View Video:</strong> You can capture your dynamic moments for more attention from both back and front. One moment, double joy.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h3>Main Camera</h3>\r\\nThe 108MP Primary Camera is Clear, Visible to Everyone. The primary camera is quite impressive and created for excellent performance. It comprises a triple-camera setup with a 108 MP (wide) PDAF primary camera, supported by a 2 MP lens and QVGA. The ultra-high pixel camera helps you to record the good life at all times. The imaging technology is upgraded again, and the automatic color gradation technology significantly improves photo transparency.\r\\n\r\\nThe Street Light Filter makes you a stand-out street photographer as you capture moments. Provide street photography master style filters to help you quickly and easily shoot a blockbuster. The primary camera is quite impressive and created for excellent performance. It comprises a triple-camera setup with a 108 MP (wide) PDAF primary camera, supported by a 2 MP lens and QVGA. The front and rear camera record decent photos. The selfie camera records 1080p@30fps videos for video capture, while the primary camera captures 4K@30fps and 1080p@30/60fps videos. Whether with family, friends or workmates, you will have a bright moment with the impressive set of cameras.\r\\n<h2>Undisputed Power in Performance</h2>\r\\n<h3>Memory Space</h3>\r\\nInfinix Note 30 VIP models have a superior space capacity of 12GB RAM and 256GB internal memory. It could not get more than this for this phone, making it stand out from the Infinix Note 30 series.\r\\n\r\\nThe new upgraded extended RAM technology can add up to 9GB RAM, and the background application retention capacity is significantly improved. Combined with up to 256GB of storage space, it is super-packable. You are unlimited with such RAM and ROM, besides microSDXC (dedicated slot) for additional memory. You stand unbothered by memory space for a long as you browse, click, save the play, and keep checking memories and moments.\r\\n<h3>Operating System</h3>\r\\nThe phone runs on the latest Android 13 OS, complemented by XOS 13 UI for optimal user experience through customization to what best suits your lifestyle and personality.\r\\n<h3>Processing Unit</h3>\r\\nPowering the Infinix Note 30 VIP is a powerful MediaTek Dimensity 8050 (6 nm) chipset. The 6nm process allows the chip to have more transistors providing ultra-efficient performance and maintaining lower power consumption. The chipset helps efficiently run background operations from the user’s commands on the multitouch screen and other tasks such as power management, multi-tasking, and enabling intelligent responses to the user.\r\\n\r\\nThe Octa-core (1×3.0 GHz Cortex-A78 &amp; 3×2.6 GHz Cortex-A78 &amp; 4×2.0 GHz Cortex-A55) CPU and Mali-G77 MC9 GPU come with the chipset. The Dimensity 8050’s octa-core CPU features four premium Arm Cortex-A78 processors, including an ‘ultra-core’ operating up to 3GHz. It can bring users faster application responsiveness, higher game frame rates, and a smoother internet connection experience.\r\\n<h4>MediaTek HyperEngine 5.0</h4>\r\\nIt provides a full range of smartphone gaming experiences, including AI-VR S variable rendering technology, Wi-Fi Bluetooth dual-link anti-interference technology, and Bluetooth LE Audio dual-link true wireless stereo with lower latency.\r\\n<h4>Ultra-Powerful Signal+WiFi 6 +Dual 5G SIM+Clever 5G 2.0</h4>\r\\nInfinix’s industry-first UPS technology dramatically improves the signal experience in gaming, short-form video, weak networks, airports, low RAT, and elevators.\r\\n<h2>Networking and Communications</h2>\r\\nInfinix Note 30 VIP is a 5G network-enabled phone. You will undoubtedly enjoy fast uploading and downloading speeds of large files and videos and seamless streaming of videos through your local telecom internet provider. It comes along with dual speakers for quality audio output. A 3.5mm jack port enables connection to a wired headset for hands-free enjoyment of your MP3 hitlist, movies, or video gaming. An FM Radio inclusion is excellent, especially if you love tuning in to your favorite FM station for news, sports, and updates.\r\\n<h4>USB Type-C 2.0, OTG enables fast data transfer, besides power charging.</h4>\r\\nFor connectivity, you can pair with other devices using the Bluetooth. NFC is also supported. Wi-Fi Connectivity enables fast internet access and usage for communication, online gaming, downloading, and uploading large files.\r\\n<h4>NFC</h4>\r\\nMultifunctional NFC Makes Life More Convenient: NFC can help you turn your phone into a bank card, traffic card, access card, and so on to meet the needs of various scenarios, making your life more convenient.\r\\n<h4>PC Connection</h4>\r\\nConnect your devices quickly in multiple ways.  Instantly transfer images, videos, or files in one step.  When connected to your PC, photos or screenshots can be synced to your computer for easy copying, pasting, or saving. For the location, GPS is installed, enabling easy tracking and finding new places.\r\\n<h2>Entertainment</h2>\r\\n<h3>Sound Output</h3>\r\\nInfinix Note 30 VIP, the overall loudness is outstanding, and the vibration is low; it has good bass with low undesirable distortion, balance timbre, good clarity, localized sound stage, and voice expression; it could reproduce natural sound quality. Overall sound quality is excellent, and Infinix NOTE 30 VIP is eligible to be branded with JBL.\r\\n\r\\nEnjoy High-level Sound Dual Speaker Sound by JBL &amp; Hi-Res. Note 30 VIP is equipped with dual stereo speakers, jointly tuned by Infinix audio team and JBL professional team to give you a professional speaker effect, and is Hi-Res certified. Gives you a cinema-quality audio experience.\r\\n<h3>Cooling off when gaming</h3>\r\\nVC Liquid Cooling keeps the Phone cold. Using a large piece of VC cooling material, the whole machine has 11 layers of cooling material, of which the VC area reaches 2890 mm.\r\\n<h3>Flagship Experience</h3>\r\\nMagnetic fluid motion graphics, new sound design, personalized design, fast and stable basic experience (application preservation, power saving mode, self-adaptation refresh rate), module basic experience optimization and iteration.\r\\n<h3>Superior Battery Capabilities</h3>\r\\nInfinix Note 30 VIP is an all-around fast-charge phone. Take charge 24/7.\r\\n<h3>Fast Charging</h3>\r\\nThe extremely 68W fast charge can charge a large 5,000mAh battery up to 80% in 1 hour.  It fast charges 1-80% fast wired recharging in 30 minutes. The battery cycles are up to 1,000 times, 25% higher than the traditional value in the mobile industry, a mark of reliability and durability. To last you through the day, the Note 30 VIP has a massive and powerful 5,000 mAh non-removable battery that shares a similar battery size to a power bank.\r\\n\r\\nA 5-minute charge can:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Give you 2.1 hours, enough time to play games</li>\r\\n 	<li>8 hours, enough time for a video game or two</li>\r\\n 	<li>6 hours, enough time to make as many calls as you need before a recharge.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h3>Wireless Fast-Charging</h3>\r\\nUse the Wireless 50W FastCharge to stay at full charge at all times. Features from a flagship phone that is as technological as it gets. Put down your phone at hand, and you can always keep your phone fully charged.\r\\n<h3>Reverse Charging</h3>\r\\nThe NOTE 30 VIP is both a phone and a charger and can be used to charge other devices via wired or wireless reverse charge in times of crisis—for example, iPhone, TWS headphones, etc.\r\\n<h3>Superior Charging set-up</h3>\r\\nUsing a charger that supports PD 3.0 agreement, you can fast charge the Note 30 VIP with improved efficiency. The current bypasses the phone’s battery and supplies power directly to the main board, effectively controlling the phone’s temperature.\r\\n\r\\nWith the aid of an AI model, it can recharge the phone up to 80% at night and fully recharge it before you wake up, helping you improve the phone’s battery life. Intelligent charging strategies and multiple security protection bring peace of mind to your charging experience and keep your handset safe.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<table id=\"tablepress-3387\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3387\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-3387-name\">\r\\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Brand</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Infinix</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Model</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Note 30 VIP</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Announced</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">June 2023</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Released</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">June 2023</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Operating System</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Android 13, XOS</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Chipset</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Mediatek Dimensity 8050 (6 nm)</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-8\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">CPU Speed</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Octa-core (1×3.0 GHz Cortex-A78 &amp; 3×2.6 GHz Cortex-A78 &amp; 4×2.0 GHz Cortex-A55)</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-9\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">GPU</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Mali-G77 MC9</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-10\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Storage</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\"><a href=\"https://www.phoneplacekenya.com/internal-storage/256gb-phones/\">256GB</a></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-11\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">RAM</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">12GB</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-12\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Card Slot</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">microSDXC (dedicated slot)</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-13\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Rear Camera</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">108 MP +