price range, the display is still sharp and vibrant, with good color accuracy and viewing angles.\r\\n\r\\nOne downside of the display is its brightness level. While the Smart 7 Plus is perfectly usable indoors, it can be difficult to see the screen in bright sunlight.\r\\n<h4>Performance and Software</h4>\r\\nUnder the hood, the Smart 7 Plus is powered by a Unisoc SC9863A1 processor, paired with Octa-core (4×1.6 GHz Cortex-A55 &amp; 4×1.2 GHz Cortex-A55) central processing unit. The phone also comes with a 4GB internal storage with a 64GB ROM ensuring that you never run out of capacity to use it. The Smart 7 Plus also comes with a 5000 mAH non removable battery capacity with 10 watts battery charger with it.\r\\n<h3>Camera</h3>\r\\nThe front camera of the Infinix smart 7 Plus is 5MP that can take decent photos and the rare camera of the phones comes with a 13MP camera couples up with a 0.3 MP. For the price range of Khs. 13,000 you are getting a fare deal with this camera phone. A great alterative to the Infinix Smart 7 Plus is the  itel S18 both phones are in the same price range and they will provide with an incredible performance.\r\\n<table id=\"tablepress-3343\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3343\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-3343-name\">\r\\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Brand</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Infinix</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Model</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Infinix Smart 7 Plus</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Announced</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>February, 2023</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Released</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>February, 2023</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Operating System</div></td>\r\\n<td cla