tails of the actor’s facial expression. 720 x 1612 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~267 ppi density) resolution gets the job done by providing a functional display for chatting, viewing videos, scanning through the gallery and gaming.\r\\n<h3>Camera Setup</h3>\r\\nThe camera setup on the Itel A05s is average for basic functionality. It features a front 5MP camera and 8MP rear-mounted primary camera. You can take basic photos and videos, leaving much to be desired if you want quality photos to share and save for remembrance.\r\\n<h3>Processing Power</h3>\r\\nBring the efficiency and performance of Itel AO5s to your work and fun moments. The upgraded Octa-Core processor takes computing to a whole new level. Combined with the Itel OS 8.6 system, it offers smoother operations and brings the latest functions to your fingertips.\r\\n\r\\nNotably, the handset comes installed with:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Unisoc SC9863A1 (28nm) chipset</li>\r\\n 	<li>Octa-core (4×1.6 GHz Cortex-A55 &amp; 4×1.2 GHz Cortex-A55) CPU</li>\r\\n 	<li>IMG8322 GPU</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nFor a level-entry smartphone, the <a href=\"https://nanoreview.net/en/soc/unisoc-sc9863a\">Unisoc SC9863A1</a> (28nm) chipset is commendable in multitasking and playing low-setting games. The performance surpasses the Itel AO4 model. Moreover, the 2GB RAM 32GB internal storage is perfect for storing applications, software and media files. Considering the handset supports MicroSD for additional memory, Itel AO5s holds its ground as a resourceful, budget smartphone.\r\\n\r\\nThe phone can hold its own for essential functions like browsing the internet, making calls and chatting on social media platforms. However, limited RAM and internally built memory limit its capability for multi-tasking, intensive use, playing games and handling heavy files.\r\\n<h3>Itel A05s Connectivity</h3>\r\\nGet ready to soar through the Internet at 4G blazing-fast speed. When streaming movies, playing online games, or video conferencing with colleagues, unlock the uninterrupted, seamless connectivity. Introduce multi-band for a more stable and reliable signal.\r\\n<h3>Increased Security</h3>\r\\nIt is important to note that Itel A05s has increased security against unauthorised access to data and files. It supports a rear-mounted Fingerprint sensor and Facial recognition LockID feature, which limits who access the phone when not in use by the owner.\r\\n<h3>Sensors</h3>\r\\nItel A05s comes with:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Rear-mounted fingerprint scanner</li>\r\\n 	<li>Accelerometer</li>\r\\n 	<li>Proximity Sensor</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h3>Battery</h3>\r\\nWith its 4,000mAh massive capacity, you can embrace extended usage time. It provides the power and flexibility you need to stay connected and productive on the go. Type-C revolutionizing the way we connect and transfer data between devices. Bringing smaller size, faster data transfer speed, and more universal compatibility.',NULL,NULL,'Itel-A05s','Itel-A05s',12000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(99,'Itel A60','Itel A60','Itel-A60','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,7,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Itel A60','<h2>Itel A60 specifications in Kenya</h2>\r\\nItel shows a sense of fashion and trend with a dual camera and lenticular texture design available in shades of blue, green, and black for its A60 Model. Moreover, the textured right-angled edges design brings a higher level of a comfortable hand feel. Safer protection with a face unlocks feature and a fingerprint sensor to keep your data and privacy safe. To shoot pictures and videos, make use of the 8MP main camera and 5MP selfie camera. Powering the handset is a 5,000mAh battery, that boasts up to 8 hours of video and browsing.\r\\n<h3>Physical Attributes of Itel A60</h3>\r\\nThe newly released budget handset by Itel measures 164 x 75.5 x 8.5 mm and weighs 184g. it is made of a plastic rear panel and body frame, and glass front. Available in Blue, Green and Black colours, Itel A60 packs a punch with a water-drop display, rear fingerpri