nch IPS LCD Display matches the expectations for such a great budget device. The big screen provides colourful pictures and images to give you impactful experiences as you enjoy video and pictures in your gallery, besides a great time gaming.\r\\n\r\\nTopping up a decent display packaging is the 500 nits of brightness which adds gloss to the 1080p resolution that helps immerse and give you unforgettable moments as you explore through your phone and connect with the rest of the world.\r\\n<h4>Camera Set up</h4>\r\\nThe latest Itel sensational handset features an impressive set of cameras. Overall, the beauty is in the eye of the beholder and the detailing of the phone plus its camera detailing emphasize as much.\r\\n<h5>Selfie Shots</h5>\r\\nUnleash the pure beauty of the scenery with enhanced highlights. Capture captivating selfies powered by a soft front flashlight and AI Beauty with the 8MP front camera\r\\n\r\\nStep in front of the lens and embrace your moment with the timely and convenient AI Portrait Selfie feature which gives the best shots ever for memories.\r\\n<h5>Main Camera</h5>\r\\nThe main camera consists of a dual set-up: 13MP HDR Camera + AI support camera.\r\\n\r\\nCapture a world with all the charm you see with your eyes\r\\n\r\\nEffortless enhancements are equally provided thanks to the camera improvements through technology. The primary camera auto-identifies scenes and enhances highlight suppression for better clear pictures effortlessly\r\\n<h4>Processing Power and Performance</h4>\r\\n<h5>Operating System</h5>\r\\nThe new OS 13 System delivers a harmonious blend of avant-garde and timeless elegance. Go ahead and enjoy a smarter, smoother experience once you power your Itel A70 on.\r\\n<h5>Powerful Core Processor</h5>\r\\nItel A7o’s performance is enhanced with a powerful Octa-core CPU integrated with the UniSoc Tiger T603 Chip.  The processing unit provides sleek intuitive operations as you navigate through the applications on the device. Enhanced performance is delivered by the greater speed and efficiency you experience with the device.\r\\n\r\\nThe Octa-core processor effortlessly tackles multitasking. Matching intensive use demands, the CPU enables you to easily navigate and switch among different apps without freezing or crushing.\r\\n<h5>Memory</h5>\r\\nThe handset comes equipped for high performance with up to 12 (4+8) GB RAM and 128GB internal memory. Extra RAM ensures your phone can handle heavy workloads and provides a seamless user experience. Notably, the 4+8GB extended RAM offers faster app start-up.\r\\n\r\\nSignificant memory consisting of boosted memory offers an increased and smooth performance as you embark on a journey of exploration, discovery and endless searches on the Itel A70. Securely store your beloved content in an extensive 128GB of space, equivalent to keeping 40,000 photos to cherish and enjoy.\r\\n\r\\nMoreover, you can expand additional memory up to 2TB thanks to the 3-Card slot available on the handset.\r\\n<h4>Enhanced Safety</h4>\r\\nExperience the ultimate convenience and security with the Dual Unlock feature on Itel A70. It combines the speed and precision of a side-mounted fingerprint sensor with effortless recognition of Face Unlock.\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Match your Usage Habits by embracing a more friendly and effortless verification process. You can unlock your device in record 355ms.</li>\r\\n 	<li>Unlock with Double Power, which elevates security and your usage convenience.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h4>Connectivity</h4>\r\\nThe device supports twin SIMs, runs on GSM / HSPA / LTE network technology and supports 2G, 3G, and 4G bands, with HSPA, LTE network speed. Although not as speedy and impressive as the 5G band, it is pretty efficient and sufficiently fast in data and file transfer (uploading and downloading).\r\\n\r\\nBesides GSM connectivity, enjoy fast and buffer-free internet connectivity thanks to the refreshing and reliable WLAN Technology (Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct) installed on Itel A70. The WLAN enables faster and safer connectivity to available Wi-Fi networks, reducing buffering due to poor connectivity.\r\\n\r\\nConnect wirelessly through Bluetooth, with the v 5.0, A2DP, LE supporting intelligent, seamless pairing with your smart devices such as Bluetooth earphones, smartwatch, Smart TV and other gadgets.\r\\n<h5>Other forms of Connectivity supported by Itel A70</h5>\r\\nNotably, Itel A70 supports:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>FM Radio</li>\r\\n 	<li>Comes with a 3.5mm jack port for connectivity with wired headsets</li>\r\\n 	<li>USB Type-C 2.0, OTG for fast, wired data transfer and connectivity via the USB port.</li>\r\\n 	<li>GPS positioning for accurate tracking and location.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h4>Communication Support</h4>\r\\nItel A70 comes installed with loudspeakers, which improve sound audibility for phone calls and when playing media.\r\\n\r\\nThe 3.5mm jack port and FM Radio support are made in heaven. You not only connect to the world by listening to your favourite radio station presentation programs and even follow broadcasts live as you commute or from remote locations where you cannot attend events in person. If you still hold dear to wired earphones, Itel A70 offers continuity of that experience.\r\\n\r\\nAdditionally, Itel installed several sensors to improve handling and enhance user experience. These sensors include\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Fingerprint (under display, optical)</li>\r\\n 	<li>Accelerometer</li>\r\\n 	<li>gyro</li>\r\\n 	<li>proximity</li>\r\\n 	<li>compass</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h4>Battery and Power Management</h4>\r\\nItel A70 features a large capacity 5,000mAh battery with a USB Type-C charger. The power on full charge is quite sufficient for long-lasting performance and efficient connectivity, either wirelessly or wired through the 3.5mm jack or USB.  The power marathon feature, with 3 energy-saving solutions ensures round-the-clock battery use.',NULL,NULL,'Itel-A70','Itel-A70',14000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(104,'Itel A70 - 128GB','Itel A70 - 128GB','Itel-A70-128GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,7,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Itel A70 - 128GB','Itel A70',NULL,NULL,'Itel-A70-128GB','Itel-A70-128GB',13500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(105,'Itel A70 - 256GB','Itel A70 - 256GB','Itel-A70-256GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,7,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Itel A70 - 256GB','Itel A70 - 128GB',NULL,NULL,'Itel-A70-256GB','Itel-A70-256GB',17000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(106,'Itel P40','Itel P40','Itel-P40','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,7,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Itel P40','<h2>Itel P40</h2>\r\\nThe Itel P40 has a 6.6-inch HD+ Dot Notch IPS display with a 90% screen-to-body ratio. On the front, there is a 5MP selfie shooter and the back has a dual 13MP main shooter and a VGA depth sensor. The phone is powered by the modest Unisoc SC9863A chipset. It has eight Cortex-A55 CPU cores running at 1.6GHz, while the GPU is PowerVR GE8322, clocked at 550MHz.\r\\n\r\\nThe phone comes with  4GB RAM with dynamic RAM and 64GB Storage options.  The Itel P40 runs Android 12 Go Edition and all this is powered by a massive 6,000 mAh battery that supports 18W charging.\r\\n<h3>Build and Design</h3>\r\\nItel P40 features an energetic and innovative design. A compact design with 3-dimensional stripes shows the combination of modernity and ingenuity. Double rings for the dual cameras inspired by a race car show a youthful attitude. The handset is more comfortable with a minimalist and symmetrical design for a stable handling experience.\r\\n<h3>Display</h3>\r\\nIndulge with the 6.6” HD+ Waterdrop Fullscreen for an immersive experience. The 1612×720 p Quad High-Definition adds 72% High Color Saturation to restore true colours. It features a 90% screen-to-body ratio that pulls you into the storyline when enjoying movies or shows.\r\\n<h3>Itel P40 Performance</h3>\r\\n<h4>Processing Unit</h4>\r\\nInstalled on the Itel P40 is an 8-core processor for ultimate performance. It is perfect for multitasking. Itel OS 8.6 improves productivity. It is your ideal partner for work and entertainment. Itel OS ascertains your privacy, entertainment, and productivity. Itel is committed to bringing you a smooth, satisfying and secure experience.\r\\n<h4>Memory Space</h4>\r\\nExperience faster experience with more space. The handset comes with 64GB+7GB (4+3) storage capacity with 3GB memory fusion for ultra-fast performance and collection of all the fun moments. Switch apps in an instant, and enjoy smoother performance.\r\\n\r\\nDepending on the model, you can have:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>64GB+7GB (4+3)</li>\r\\n 	<li>64GB + 4GB</li>\r\\n 	<li>32GB + 6GB RAM</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nWith such RAM and internal storage, you can store up to 26,000 photos, 18,000 short videos, 600 TV Episodes, and 200 Movies and have 48-72 apps running simultaneously.\r\\n<h3>Camera set up</h3>\r\\nCapture life’s incredible moments and detailed videos using the front-facing and main camera that comprises a 13MP + AI Depth Sensor at the back of the phone. P40 captures exhilarating moments with a 13MP rear camera, delivering crisp and clear image details as you see in reality. Using the Panorama Mode, capture every scene entirely as you see it. Use the Time-lapse Mode to tell a story about movement. Use the Pro Mode to become the next professional photographer.\r\\n<h3>Battery</h3>\r\\nA 6,000mAh Li-Po non-removable Mega Battery powers up your whole day. A more robust battery performance with AI Power Master enables longer-lasting entertainment and social experience. Always stay online and connected to the world.\r\\n\r\\nThe battery is built to adapt to the user’s lifestyle intelligently. A full charge can last up to 57 days on standby, 32 hours of continuous talk and 204 hours of continuous music playback. It supports 28 hours of video playback, 16 hours of gaming and 21 hours of messaging.\r\\n\r\\nSupporting fast charging, the charging system comes packed with an 18W fast charger. The battery is fully charged in under 2.5 hours. Say goodbye to battery anxiety.',NULL,NULL,'Itel-P40','Itel-P40',14000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(107,'Itel P55','Itel P55','Itel-P55','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,7,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Itel P55','<h2>Itel P55 4G Specifications</h2>\r\\nItel P55 is a budget smartphone that has a 6.6-inch HD+ display with a 90Hz refresh rate, a 50MP AI dual rear camera, and an 8MP selfie camera. Itel P55 4G runs on a Unisoc Tiger T606 processor with 8GB of RAM and Android 13 operating system. In comparison, the Itel P55 5G model runs on a MediaTek Dimensity 6080 processor with 6GB of RAM and the Itel OS 13 interface. The device P55 has a 5,000mAh battery with 18W fast charging, a side-mounted fingerprint sensor, and a vegan leather finish.\r\\n\r\\nNotable Features of the Itel P55 4G Model are:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li> <strong>Display</strong>: It features a 6.6-inch HD+ IPS LCD screen with a 90Hz refresh rate and a resolution of 720 x 1612 pixels.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Processor</strong>: The phone is powered by the Unisoc T606 chipset (12 nm) with an octa-core CPU (2×1.6 GHz Cortex-A75 &amp; 6×1.6 GHz Cortex-A55) and a Mali-G57 MP1 GPU.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Memory</strong>: It comes in three variants: 128GB storage with 4GB RAM, 128GB storage with 8GB RAM, and 256GB storage with 8GB RAM.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Camera</strong>:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li><em>Rear Camera:</em> A 50 MP primary camera and a 0.08 MP auxiliary lens. It supports features like dual-LED flash and can record videos in 1080p.</li>\r\\n 	<li><em>Selfie Camera</em>: An 8 MP front camera.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Connectivity</strong>: It supports GSM, HSPA, and LTE networks.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Battery</strong>: The phone has a 5000 mAh non-removable battery that supports 18W wired charging. For 10 minutes of fasting charging, you gain 3 hours of continuous chatting.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Other Features</strong>:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Dual SIM</strong> (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Fingerprint sensor</strong> (side-mounted)</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>USB Type-C: </strong>wired connectivity and charging.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n</li>\r\\n</ul>',NULL,NULL,'Itel-P55','Itel-P55',17000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(108,'Itel S23','Itel S23','Itel-S23','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,7,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Itel S23','<h2>Itel S23 specification in Kenya</h2>\r\\nThe Itel S23 features a large feature 6.6-inch IPS Display HD display with a 90Hz refresh rate. The phone comes with a dual 50-megapixel rear camera and a 5-megapixel front-facing camera for videos and selfies. It has a 64GB or 128GB of internal storage that can be expanded to 128GB via microSD card and is powered by a Unisoc T606 quad-core processor. The phone’s unique feature is the 8GB RAM with Memory Fusion meaning it has a 4GB that can be upgraded to 8GB. The Itel S23 is available in colors Mystery White, and Starry Black color options.\r\\n<h2>Itel S23 Specifications</h2>\r\\n<table id=\"tablepress-3446\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3446\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-3446-name\">\r\\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Brand</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">itel</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Model</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">itel S23</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Announced</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">May, 2023</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Released</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">June, 2023</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Operating System</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Android 12</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">Chipset</td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">UNISOC Tiger T606 (12 nm)</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-8\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">CPU Speed</td>\r