b more efficiently. Its side-mounted fingerprint scanner is fast and accurate. The scanner combines well with facial recognition for unlocking the device and enhances security access to your phone. The handset has a USB-C port for wired data transfer, charging, and expandable storage via a microSD card slot. Connectivity and communication are enhanced by the Bluetooth installed for pairing, besides Wi-Fi connectivity (Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct), accurate positioning (GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, BDS, QZSSPS), and NFC. The Samsung Galaxy A15 4G supports FM Radio and a 3.5mm jack port.\r\\n<h4>Battery Life</h4>\r\\nThe powerful and large capacity 5,000mAh battery is a significant highlight for the Samsung Galaxy A15. As an average user, you will have at least 1.5 days of usage time before recharging. Samsung’s One UI includes power-saving features that can help stretch the battery life further. To recharge, use the 15W wired fast charging unit that gets you going quickly.',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G','Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G',25500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(189,'Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 4GB','Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 4GB','Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G-4GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 4GB','Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 4GB',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G-4GB','Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G-4GB',25500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(190,'Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 6GB','Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 6GB','Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G-6GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 6GB','Samsung Galaxy A15 4G - 6GB',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G-6GB','Samsung-Galaxy-A15-4G-6GB',29000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(191,'Samsung Galaxy A24','Samsung Galaxy A24','Samsung-Galaxy-A24','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy A24','<h2>Samsung Galaxy A24 in Kenya</h2>\r\\nThe Samsung Galaxy A24  is powered by the Mediatek MT8781 Helio G99 (6nm). T