s buffering).\r\\n<h3>Wired Connectivity</h3>\r\\nWired connectivity is fundamental to any smartphone. Samsung Galaxy S24+, a modern high-end smartphone, comes installed with a high-tech, more enhanced USB Type-C 3.2, OTG for wired connectivity. USB Type-C 3.2, OTG offers faster data transfer speeds and supports more power modes than USB-C. It preserves existing USB 3.1 and SuperSpeed+ data modes while supporting two-lane operation, doubling the data rates to 10 and 20 Gbit/s (1 and ~2.4 GB/s).\r\\n\r\\nOther forms of wireless connectivity you can enjoy include:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>NFC</li>\r\\n 	<li>GPS, GLONASS, BDS, GALILEO</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h3>Sensors</h3>\r\\nAs a high-end smartphone, it comes with a wide array of sensors that enhance the handling and user experience when using the handset. The sensors include:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Fingerprint (under display, ultrasonic), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer;</li>\r\\n 	<li>Samsung DeX, Samsung Wireless DeX (desktop experience support);</li>\r\\n 	<li>Ultra-wideband (UWB) support.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h3>Battery</h3>\r\\nPowering the handset is a Li-Ion 4,900mAh, non-removable battery, which provides a day charge, depending on usage intensity. You can now:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Watch videos: 29 hours</li>\r\\n 	<li>Listen to Music: 88 hours</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nThe device supports:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>45W wired, PD3.0, 65% in 30 min</li>\r\\n 	<li>15W wireless (Qi/PMA) charging.</li>\r\\n 	<li>5W reverse wireless charging.</li>\r\\n</ul>',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G',200000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(208,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 256GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 256GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G-256GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 256GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 256GB',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G-256GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G-256GB',200000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(209,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 512GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 512GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G-512GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 512GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Plus 5G - 512GB',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G-512GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Plus-5G-512GB',230000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(210,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra','Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra','<h2>Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra Specifications in Kenya</h2>\r\\nSamsung Galaxy S24 Ultra 5G price in Kenya is Ksh 235,000. The device has a 6.8-inch 120Hz Dynamic AMOLED 2X display with a screen resolution of 1440 x 3088 pixels and is protected by Corning Gorilla Glass Armor. It is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor with Adreno 750 GPU. The phone has 12GB RAM and 256 GB of internal storage. It runs on Android 14 with Samsung One UI 6.1, powered by a 5,000 mAh battery with 45W fast charging.\r\\n\r\\nS24 Ultra packs a quad rear camera setup with a massive 200 MP main sensor, a 12 MP ultra wide-angle camera, a 10 MP telephoto camera, a 50 MP periscope telephoto camera, and on the front, there is a 12MP selfie camera. It comes in Titanium Black, Titanium Gray, Titanium Violet\r\\n<h3>Product Description</h3>\r\\n<h4>Design and Build</h4>\r\\nMeet Galaxy S24 Ultra, the ultimate form of Galaxy Ultra with a new titanium exterior, a 6.8-inch flat Gorilla Glass display, and a glass back (Gorilla Glass). It is an absolute marvel of design. The handset, 162.3 x 79 x 8.6 mm (6.39 x 3.11 x 0.34 in), weighs 232g. it is a massive smartphone with matching weight, which is reasonable compared to the dimensions and weight of rival brands such as Google Pixel, Apple, and Huawei. The device supports Nano-SIM and eSIM/ Dual eSIM or Dual SIM (2 Nano-SIMs and eSIM, dual stand-by). It is IP68 dust/water resistant (up to 1.5m for 30 min) and supports a Stylus Pen (Bluetooth integration, accelerometer, gyro).\r\\n<h5>Key Features</h5>\r\\n<h6>Armor up with titanium.</h6>\r\\nCheck out the upgrade — a durable shield of titanium built right into the frame. The strength of titanium is now at your fingertips.\r\\n<h6>Built-in S Pen</h6>\r\\nThe legacy of Galaxy Note is alive and well. Write, tap, and navigate with the precision your fingers wish they had on the new, flat display.\r\\n<h6>Corning Glass protection</h6>\r\\nBetter scratch resistance with Corning Gorilla Armor installed at the front and back of the Galaxy S24 Ultra.\r\\n<h6>Water Resistance</h6>\r\\nWorry less about splashes and dust messing up your pricey and precious device. It comes with the IP68 dust/water resistant (up to 1.5m for 30 min). At least, you can be less anxious and worried even when caught up in a storm, or your Galaxy S24 Ultra accidentally slips into a swimming pool or water puddle. You can still retrieve it, wipe off the water, and enjoy the incredible experience of owning it.\r\\n<h6>Colors</h6>\r\\nSamsung Galaxy S24 Ultra comes in various classic, elegant colors. You can pick from:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Black</li>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Gray</li>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Violet</li>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Yellow</li>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Blue</li>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Green</li>\r\\n 	<li>Titanium Orange variants.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h4>Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra Display</h4>\r\\nEnjoy the awesome 6.8-inch, 113.5 cm<sup>2</sup> (~88.5% screen-to-body ratio) display of the Galaxy S24 Ultra. The Dynamic LTPO AMOLED 2X, 120Hz, HDR10+, 2600 nits (peak) display is one of a kind for the most cinematic viewing experience ever. Boasting an impressive 1440 x 3120 pixels, 19.5:9 ratio (~505 ppi density) resolution, displays cannot be better than this for high-quality videos and picture viewing, whether indoors or outdoors.\r\\n\r\\nThe 2600-nit display is Samsung’s brightest adaptive mobile display under the sun. Samsung’s most immersive display comes with some significant visibility upgrades. Corning Gorilla Armor reduces reflections and improves visual clarity, even in direct sunlight. Then, an improved Vision Booster enhances contrast and color for an exceptional experience.\r\\n<h4>Phone Performance</h4>\r\\n<h5>Operating System</h5>\r\\nThe premium handset comes installed with Android 14 OS, supported by Samsung’s One UI 6.1 cover for customization.\r\\n<h5>Processor</h5>\r\\nThe Samsung handset has an Octa-core <a href=\"https://www.qualcomm.com/products/mobile/snapdragon/smartphones/snapdragon-8-series-mobile-platforms/snapdragon-8-gen-3-mobile-platform\">Qualcomm SM8650-AC Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 (4 nm)</a> processor. The processor enables you to achieve new-found creativity using generative AI, intelligently capture unique content, get lost in console-defying mobile gaming, or jam out untethered to studio-quality lossless audio—all backed by 5G (the world’s fastest mobile connectivity).\r\\n\r\\nThe powerful Qualcomm AI Engine infuses brilliance into your every move, from drafting documents to intelligently creating one-of-a-kind content. LLM models can run up to 20 tokens/sec – one of the fastest in the smartphone industry, and, with stable diffusion, generate an image in a fraction of a second. Snapdragon makes the impossible possible by using a new era of generative AI.\r\\n\r\\nPrepare to be mesmerized by gameplay with Snapdragon Game Super Resolution upscaling games as high as 8K without impacting battery life or performance. Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 is your ultimate portable gaming console. The ultra-intelligent Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 redefines your experience with premium-level photography, gaming, audio, and beyond performance.\r\\n<h5>Phone Storage</h5>\r\\nEnjoy ample, unlimited phone storage on the Galaxy S24 Ultra. The handset comes installed with internal memory comprising of the following:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>256GB 12GB RAM</li>\r\\n 	<li>512GB 12GB RAM</li>\r\\n 	<li>1TB 12GB RAM (all with UFS 4.0 technology)</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n12GB RAM clearly distinguishes the Samsung handset as a high-end, high-performance smartphone made for intensive tasks and capable of fast data processing. Access to UP TO 1TB ROM is comforting, especially if you have lots of large files that you want to be stored nearby and accessible for perusing, sharing, or working on at short notice. You can thus save it all on the 256GB/512GB/1TB without worrying much about running out of memory or lagging in the case of limited RAM.\r\\n<h6>Samsung UFS 4.0</h6>\r\\nTransitioning from UFS 3.0, <a href=\"https://semiconductor.samsung.com/estorage/ufs/ufs-4-0/\">UFS 4.0</a> offers even better speeds and efficiency. The flash storage is built for a more innovative, slimmer, and powerful mobile era, such as what Galaxy S24 Ultra offers. With a massive 1TB capacity, it delivers double the speed of the previous generation and 45% better efficiency – removing speed bottlenecks.\r\\nFor faster smartphone operations, smoother VR, and more responsive driving experiences.\r\\n\r\\nThe UFS 4.0 fits perfectly for blazing fast 5G, supercharged app performance, and industry-beating read-write speeds. It comes with a unique controller built and designed by Samsung, using powerful 176-layer 7th Generation V-NAND to deliver 4,200MBps read speeds, while MIPI M-PHY 5.0 offers up 23.2Gbps data transfers – doubling the speed of UFS 3.1. Even write speeds get a 1.6x bump to 2,800MBps, so your users can work, play, and create without limits.\r\\n<h6>RPMB security solution technology WITH X1.8 times enhanced performance</h6>\r\\nYour most intimate data is stored on your phone. UFS 4.0 protects it from attacks with Advanced RPMB (Replay Protected Memory Block). UFS 4.0 is 1.8 times better at protecting data than the previous generation, so passwords, IDs, and your favorite memories all have a safe place to stay.\r\\n<h5>Knox Matrix</h5>\r\\nRest easy with Samsung’s unparalleled mobile protection, fortified by the impenetrable Knox Matrix with multi-device security. Your data, privacy, and peace of mind are our top priorities.\r\\n<h5>Mobile Gaming</h5>\r\\nSamsung Galaxy S24 Ultra has the most hyper-realistic mobile gameplay yet on any smartphone handset. Victory can be yours with the new Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 for Galaxy. Faster processing gives you the power you need for all the gameplay you want. Then, manifest graphic effects in real-time with ray tracing for hyper-realistic shadows and reflections.\r\\n<h6>Heat Control</h6>\r\\nSamsung has nearly doubled the size of Galaxy S24 Ultra’s Vapor Chamber to improve heat dissipation and give you the smooth graphics experience it intended.\r\\n<h4>iOS and Galaxy Seamless Switching</h4>\r\\n<h5>Quick Share</h5>\r\\nYou are not limited to Galaxy phones. Use QR codes and saved contacts to share with iOS users or far-away friends and family.\r\\n<h5>Why Switch from iOS to Galaxy?</h5>\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Switch effortlessly from iOS</strong>: Keep your photos, contacts, calendar, and apps with Smart Switch — even if you switch from iOS</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Trailblaze the AI frontier: </strong>Switch to Galaxy to make your day effortless through the new era of mobile AI with Galaxy AI.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Forget barriers between devices: </strong>Switch to Galaxy to open up seamless ways to work, play, and stay healthy across your devices.</li>\r\\n 	<li><strong>Share files now: </strong>Effortlessly send photos, videos, and files to users outside the Galaxy ecosystem through Quick Share. Previously an exclusive among Galaxy devices, it also works with nearby Androids.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h4> Camera Setup</h4>\r\\nEnjoy a top-notch, Industry-leading camera, now enhanced with AI.\r\\n<h5>Selfie Camera</h5>\r\\nCapture high-quality 12 MP, f/2.2, 26mm (wide), Dual Pixel PDAF front-facing lens. The camera is well equipped for dual video calls and comes with Auto-HDR and HDR10+ features to optimize pictures and videos. Besides enabling you to capture fantastic photos, it also records 4K@30/60fps and 1080p@30fps videos.\r\\n<h5> Main Camera</h5>\r\\nGalaxy S24 Ultra comes installed with a quad main camera set-up consisting of:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>200 MP, f/1.7, 24mm (wide), 1/1.3″, 0.6µm, multi-directional PDAF, Laser AF, OIS</li>\r\\n 	<li>50 MP, f/3.4, 111mm (periscope telephoto), PDAF, OIS, 5x optical zoom</li>\r\\n 	<li>10 MP, f/2.4, 67mm (telephoto), 1/3.52″, 1.12µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, OIS, 3x optical zoom</li>\r\\n 	<li>12 MP, f/2.2, 13mm, 120˚ (ultrawide), 1/2.55″, 1.4µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, Super Steady video</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h6>Powerful Primary lens</h6>\r\\nWith the most megapixels on a smartphone and AI processing, Galaxy S24 Ultra sets the industry standard for image quality every time you hit the shutter. Moreover, the new ProVisual engine recognizes objects — improving color tone, reducing noise, and bringing out detail.\r\\n<h6>ProVisual engine shoots every night in precise detail</h6>\r\\nSpace Zoom puts you in the middle of the action, even at night. With 1.6x larger pixels and a wider Tele OIS, photos and videos are brighter and more stable — making even distant subjects stunning.\r\\n<h6>Samsung’s most potent Quad Tele zoom yet</h6>\r\\nDo not let long distances get you down. Now you can get 2x, 3x, 5x, and even 10x close-ups with optical or optical quality zoom. The new, powerful Tele OIS is more comprehensive to stabilize the shot for less zoom-in blur.\r\\n<h4>Galaxy AI is here.</h4>\r\\nWelcome to the era of mobile AI. With Galaxy S24 Ultra in your hands, you can unleash new levels of creativity, productivity, and possibility — starting with the most essential device in your life, your smartphone—Epic just like that.\r\\n<h5>Digital Zoom closes in, and AI Zoom amps it up.</h5>\r\\nGo from scenic to specific thanks to deep learning-based AI Zoom. Glide seamlessly past 1x zoom to 100x zoom while AI amps up the details at all the points in between\r\\n<h5>Super HDR. AI from preview to post</h5>\r\\nWith Samsung’s latest Super HDR upgrade, camera previews display Super HDR like your final capture. You can immediately see what your super-vivid photos and videos will look like before you even take them. Plus, it even works when you’re shooting with social media app cameras.\r\\n<h5>Resize it, Retouch it. Just like that</h5>\r\\nSomething out of place? Could you just move it to the post? New AI-powered editing options let you get the photo you wanted, like relocating objects and intelligently filling in the space they left behind.\r\\n<h5>Could you circle it and find it? Just like that</h5>\r\\nA new way to search is here with Circle to Search. While scrolling your favorite social network, use your S Pen or finger to circle something and get Google Search results.\r\\n\r\\nStumble upon a photo of a beautiful plant that you have to know what it is. Circle it, and ta-da, you’ll get Google Search results. Now, you can quickly get an answer without leaving your feed.\r\\n<h5>Live Translate. The easiest way to communicate</h5>\r\\nThanks to Live Translate, you can now get real-time interpretation while on the phone.  Break down language barriers like never before — even through messaging. Reply in your language — it’ll also get translated on their end.\r\\n<h5>Pick the right tone for your text with Chat Assist</h5>\r\\nCompose text messages with AI at the helm in Chat Assist. Now you can say what you mean with the voice of a professional, a close friend, even just politely. Go from “How do I say this?” to “Why didn’t I think of that?” in seconds.\r\\n<h5>Summarise Notes in the blink of an AI</h5>\r\\nWhether you’re typing up a storm or jotting something down, Note Assist makes a long story short. Could you start writing and format it into a clear, easy-to-review summary later?\r\\n\r\\nAnd when you’re looking for an old note, the new covers show simple summaries — keeping your screen organized so you can easily find things.\r\\n<h4>Communication and Connectivity</h4>\r\\n<h5>Speakers</h5>\r\\nEnjoy seamless connectivity and seamless communication on the Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra. The handset comes with stereo speakers for quality audio output. Like other high-end Samsung devices, it has no 3.5mm jack but comes with 32-bit/384kHz audio, tuned by AKG for audio streaming. Bluetooth connectivity offers an even better alternative than the omitted wired connectivity, allowing you to enjoy ANC, Bluetooth calls, and transparency Modes on your headphones or earphones, depending on their specifications and capabilities.\r\\n<h5>5G Network Connectivity</h5>\r\\nGalaxy S24 Ultra is 5G enabled. Use the latest GSM/CDMA/HSPA/EVDO/LTE/5G network technology for fast, seamless connectivity, whether making phone calls, video calls, or accessing data. You can access 2G, 3G, 4G, and 5G Network bandwidths, depending on the availability and strength of the signal by your local service provider. Maximize fully on the HSPA, LTE-A (up to 7CA), and 5G network speeds for seamless videos, uploading and downloading of files, and sustained high-quality video communications without worrying about buffering and slow-down speed. Live streaming of events is now more fun as you update or remain updated on ongoing important events within or in distant locations.\r\\n<h5>Bluetooth</h5>\r\\nAs mentioned earlier, Bluetooth connectivity has developed to become a mainstay. The Galaxy phone comes installed with the latest Bluetooth v5.3, A2DP, and LE, ensuring fast, safe, and intelligent connectivity with your smart devices to keep you remotely connected as you do your business at home while commuting, driving, or in the office.\r\\n<h5>GPS Tracking</h5>\r\\nGPS, GLONASS, BDS, and GALILEO ensure accurate location and tracking of any part of the world. As you travel and venture into new frontiers, the GPS enables easy monitoring, establishing your location or guiding you through unfamiliar neighborhoods as you drive. If you get lost, you can be easily tracked.\r\\n<h5>USB Wired Connectivity</h5>\r\\nAs gadgets go high-tech, wired connectivity remains important to handsets. Galaxy S24 Ultra comes along with USB Type-C 3.2 and OTG. The USB is enhanced to deliver more data and power faster than previous USB Type C versions. While it preserves the existing USB 3.1 SuperSpeed USB Type-C 3.2, OTG introduces two new SuperSpeed+ transfer modes over the USB-C connector using two-lane operation, doubling the data rates to 10 and 20 Gbit/s (1 and ~2.4 GB/s).\r\\n<h4>Sensors</h4>\r\\nAs expected, the handset has various sensors to improve the handling experience. These include Fingerprint (under display, ultrasonic), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, and barometer. Samsung DeX and Samsung Wireless DeX provide desktop experience support, making the device more adaptable for productive use in an office setup.\r\\n<h4>Battery and Power Management</h4>\r\\nEnjoy an all-day battery to play on and on. With a massive 5,000mAh battery capacity and greater energy efficiency, Galaxy S24 Ultra’s battery gives you an extra life when it matters most —like the epic boss battle you have been gearing up for. You can:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Watch videos for up to 30 hours</li>\r\\n 	<li>Listen to music for up to 95 hours</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nRecharge the Li-Ion 5000 mAh, non-removable battery using:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Wired Charging 45W wired, PD3.0, 65% in 30 minutes</li>\r\\n 	<li>15W wireless (Qi/PMA)</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nYou can equally recharge your smartwatch, wireless earphones, or other handset with the 4.5W reverse wireless charging unit that brings along convenience and saves you the trouble of plugging into a wall power source.',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra',238999,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(211,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 256GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 256GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-256GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 256GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 256GB',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-256GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-256GB',238999,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(212,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 512GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 512GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-512GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 512GB','Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra - 512GB',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-512GB','Samsung-Galaxy-S24-Ultra-512GB',254999,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(213,'Samsung Galaxy Watch 4','Samsung Galaxy Watch 4','Samsung-Galaxy-Watch-4','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy Watch 4','<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\"><h2>Samsung Galaxy Watch 4 in Kenya</h2><p><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">The Samsung Galaxy Watch 4 price is Ksh 30',NULL,NULL,'Samsung-Galaxy-Watch-4','Samsung-Galaxy-Watch-4',21500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(214,'Samsung Galaxy Z Flip4','Samsung Galaxy Z Flip4','Samsung-Galaxy-Z-Flip4','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,2,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Samsung Galaxy Z Flip4','<h1>Galaxy Z Flip 4 5G in Kenya</h1>\r\\nThe Samsung Galaxy Z Flip4 is powered by an Octa-core Qualcomm SM8475 Snapdragon 8+ Gen 1 (4 nm) processor. While using the UFS 3.1 Technology to maximize the internalized space, the Flip 4 comes with an internal space of 128GB 8GB RAM / 256GB 8GB RAM / 512GB 8GB RAM. The handset runs on Android 12 and is powered by 3,700mAh and a 25W wired fast charger. Enjoy awesome snaps and video captures through a 10 MP, f/2.4, 26mm (wide) selfie camera and a powerful dual rear camera set-up comprising of a 12MP (wide)+12MP (Ultra-wide) camera. The device is available in a wide range of colors: Bora Purple, Graphite, Pink Gold, Blue\r\\n<h3>Design, Body, and Display</h3>\r\\nSamsung Galaxy Z Flip4 is a high-end handset created with both luxury and functionality in mind while using the latest technology to set it apart. The device is designed to clap back and looks good whether unfolded for use or folded to be tucked away in the pocket. It is made of Plastic front (opened), glass back (Gorilla Glass Victus+), and aluminum frame. Weighing 187g, the Flip 4 measures 84.9 x 71.9 x 15.9-17.1 mm when folded and 165.2 x 71.9 x 6.9 mm (unfolded).\r\\n\r\\nThe foldable, dynamic AMOLED 2X display measures 6.7-inches and has a refresh rate of 120Hz, and 1200 nits (peak brightness). The Cover display of the foldable device is Super AMOLED, and 1.9 inches in size. The resolution on the 6.7-inch display is 1080 x 2640 pixels, and 260 x 512 pixels on the cover display, which is protected by Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+.\r\\n<h3>Processing Unit</h3>\r\\nSamsung Galaxy Z Flip4 is a premium handset with multiple premium features. It is equipped o operate optimally with the latest technology in terms of the operating system, display, and processing unit. It runs on the latest Android, Android 12. The One UI 4.1.1 enables smooth and excellent user interactivity with the handset.  It is powered by a powerful and dynamic Octa-core, Octa-core (1×3.19 GHz Cortex-X2 &amp; 3×2.75 GHz Cortex-A710 &amp; 4×1.80 GHz Cortex-A510) processing unit on a reliable and efficient Qualcomm SM8475 Snapdragon 8+ Gen 1 (4 nm) chipset and Adreno 730 Graphic Processing Unit.  The processing unit overall is one of the most powerful available in mobile technology, making it easy for you to work productivity, multitask, browse the internet, play games and even live stream videos with no difficulties on the Flip Z.\r\\n<h3>Memory Space</h3>\r\\nSamsung put much effort into ensuring optimal internal memory on the handset for users. They provide several options for users to pick from, based on their needs, budget, and other preferences. The Samsung Galaxy Z Flip 4 comes in several variants: 128GB 8GB RAM / 256GB 8GB RAM / 512GB 8GB RAM. Both the RAM and ROM are sufficient to run the core software and other downloaded applications without running out of memory space. There is no need for a dedicated MicroSD slot, hence its omission.\r\\n<h3>Battery</h3>\r\\nThe handset is powered by a 3,700mAh non-removable battery. The battery is kind of limited in an age where battery size and life is a huge determinants in customer choices on handsets to buy and own. Considering the device is power-hungry, three charging offers are provided for the same.\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Fast charging 25W (wired adapter)</li>\r\\n 	<li>Fast wireless charging 15W</li>\r\\n 	<li>Reverse wireless charging 4.5W</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nWith these three charging options, besides an intelligent system that maximizes on battery power consumption, you can carry on your activities with no worries or inconveniences due to low or no power.\r\\n<h3>Camera.</h3>\r\\nThe selfie camera comprises a single 10 MP, f/2.4, 26mm (wide), 1.22µm camera. The front camera can capture 4K videos at @30fps. At the back, the device packs a dual camera set-up comprising 12 MP, f/1.8, 24mm (wide), 1/1.76″, 1.8µm, Dual Pixel PDAF, OIS + 12 MP, f/2.2, 123˚ (ultra-wide), 1.12µm lenses. Cameras are not the strongest points of the Flip 4, but they will get the job done when it comes to video capture and taking pictures.\r\\n<h3>Sensors</h3>\r\\nSamsung Galaxy Z Flip4 features various sensors. They include Fingerprint (side-mounted), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass and barometer.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<table id=\"tablepress-3140\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3140\" aria-describedby=\"tablepress-3140-description\">\r\\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Brand</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Samsung</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Model</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Galaxy Z Flip 4</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Announced</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>August 2022</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr cla