lumn-1\">\r\\n<div>Bluetooth</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">5.2, A2DP, LE</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-22\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>GPS</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Dual-band A-GPS, GLONASS</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-23\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>NFC</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Yes</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-24\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Wi-Fi</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n, dual-band</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-25\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>USB</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>USB Type-C 2.0, OTG</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-26\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Radio</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>FM radio</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-27\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Sensor</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">Fingerprint (under display, optical), accelerometer, proximity, compass</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-28\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Battery</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">\r\\n<div>Li-Po 5000 mAh, non-removable</div></td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n<tr class=\"row-29\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r\\n<div>Fast Charging</div></td>\r\\n<td class=\"column-2\">33W wired</td>\r\\n</tr>\r\\n</tbody>\r\\n</table>',NULL,NULL,'Tecno-Camon-20-Pro-5G','Tecno-Camon-20-Pro-5G',46000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(221,'Tecno Phantom V FOLD','Tecno Phantom V FOLD','Tecno-Phantom-V-FOLD','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,3,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Tecno Phantom V FOLD','<h2>Tecno Phantom V FOLD specifications in Kenya</h2>\r\\n<h3>Design and Build</h3>\r\\nAs a foldable handset, Tecno Phantom V Fold is a masterpiece of engineering. It weighs 299g, measures 159.4 x 72 x 14.2-14.5 mm when folded and 159.4 x 140.4 x 6.9 mm (when unfolded). The Phantom V Fold is Dual SIM, supporting Nano-SIM, dual stand-by. It has no MicroSD slot, hence maximizing the slots for the SIM cards. An Aramid Fiber Protective Case is exclusively designed for the Tecno Phantom V Fold. You will find the case handy for hands-off viewing of the handset on your desktop, with the retrievable stand a useful addition.\r\\n<h3>Tecno Phantom V FOLD Display</h3>\r\\nBoth the 7.85-inch ultra-flat main screen and the curved 6.42-inch curved sub-screen define the Tecno Phantom V Fold. The 120 optimally-sized flagship dual screen is impressive and immersive both on the inside and outside. The 7.85-inch ultra-flat foldable main screen is virtually crease free, enabling you to unfold endless possibilities on the ultra-big main screen. Entertainment or work, you will be immersed the moment you turn the display on.\r\\n\r\\nNotable the 7.85-inch ultra-flat main screen has:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>8:7 optimally -sized main screen</li>\r\\n 	<li>Flexible AMOLED display</li>\r\\n 	<li>2k+ Resolution / 2000 x 2296 pixels (~388 ppi density)</li>\r\\n 	<li>90% screen-to-body ratio</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nWhen folded, you will have uninterrupted access to a 6.42-inch curved sub-screen, which fits perfectly in your palm.  The classic 21:9 ultra-big display with the unique, micro-curved design provides a second screen for calls, quick chats and use of the handset without unfolding it up.\r\\n\r\\nNotable on the 6.42-inch curved sub-screen are:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Optimally-sized sub-screen</li>\r\\n 	<li>Flexible AMOLED display</li>\r\\n 	<li>1080p resolution / 1080 x 2550 pixels, 431 PPI</li>\r\\n 	<li>1% screen-to-body ratio.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nThe Aerospace-grade Innovative Hinge is virtually crease-fee, with the screen crease measuring 0.11 mm. Re-imagine the foldable from every dimension that can be imagined, whether in size, material, or groundbreaking-hinge design. The Phantom V Fold was designed to be exceptional. Made from aerospace-grade materials, the hinge boasts an innovative proprietary hinge design, providing a crease-free screen with high durability of over 200,000 folds. It is lightweight yet strong. Folded, it fits tightly. Unfolded, it leaves no noticeable creases.\r\\n<h3>Tecno Phantom V FOLD Camera</h3>\r\\nAn ultra-clear 5 lenses camera system defines the Tecno Phantom V Fold, enabling it to rise above boundaries. The rear camera consists of a triple setup:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>50 MP, f/1.9, (wide), 1/1.3″, PDAF (primary camera</li>\r\\n 	<li>50 MP, (telephoto), PDAF, 2x optical zoom (portrait camera)</li>\r\\n 	<li>13 MP, 120˚ (ultrawide)</li>\r\\n 	<li>4K@30fps, 1080p@30fps video recording</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nThe 50MP main camera with superlight custom sensors is specifically enabled to capture the minutest of details to retain every exquisite nuance. Super Night Portrait, Super Night Mode and Super Night 4K video are the main highlights when using the main camera. With the 50MP Night Camera, you can capture virtually any glamourous moment, especially in the dark. The front-facing cameras open new [photography experiences for the users. Capture ultra selfies and use the sub-screen for a preview.\r\\n\r\\nThe front-facing cameras consist of:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>16 MP, (wide) Main Screen Camera</li>\r\\n 	<li>32 MP, (wide) UHD Sub Screen Camera</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h3>Operating System, Processing Unit &amp; Inbuild Memory</h3>\r\\nThe Phantom Fold phone runs on Android 13 OS. The operating system is complemented with HiOS 13-Fold skin which is instrumental in improving the user experience. The handset’s flagship MediaTek Dimensity 9000+ (4 nm) chipset leads in performance and power at the core. Specifically, the chipset provides higher performance, lower power consumption, better thermal control, and seamless multi-tasking on the large screen.\r\\n\r\\nRunning apps simultaneously? Playing a high-setting video game? Have no worries, considering the high-performance MediaTek Dimensity 9000+ chipset, coupled with the efficient Octa-core (1×3.20 GHz Cortex-X2 &amp; 3×2.85 GHz Cortex-A710 &amp; 4×1.80 GHz Cortex-A510) CPU and Mali-G710 MC10 GPU. A 12GB LPDDR5X RAM is quite a statement of intent on performance by Tecno, on the Phantom Fold model. Such high RAM enables ultra-high data transfer, with a theoretical speed of up to 20%. An inbuilt space memory of 256GB / 512GB (with UFS 3.1 technology) provides a base for ultra-high-speed data reading, sequentially faster by 100%.\r\\n<h3>Sensors</h3>\r\\nInstalled on the Phantom fold are:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Fingerprint (side-mounted)</li>\r\\n 	<li>Accelerometer</li>\r\\n 	<li>Gyro</li>\r\\n 	<li>proximity</li>\r\\n 	<li>compass sensors</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nthe fingerprint sensor is side-mounted and integrated into the power key. You can unlock your phone with your intuitive touch, with your biometrics enhancing security on who accesses data and information stored on your handset.\r\\n<h3>Tecno Phantom V FOLD Network</h3>\r\\nTecno Phantom V Fold is 5G enabled. It relies on GSM / HSPA / LTE / 5G network technology. Supporting 2G, 3G, 4G and 5G network bands, the device takes up HSPA, LTE, 5G network speed. thus, you are assured of fast uploading and downloading of heavy files and data.\r\\n<h3>Connectivity and Communications</h3>\r\\nInstalled on the device are Dual Stereo Speakers, which provide the immersive stereo sound effect. For connectivity, make use of Bluetooth (5.2, A2DP, LE), and WLAN (Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band). To transfer data, make use of USB Type-C, OTG, and NFC, whereas FM Radio is supported by the device, a 3.5mm jack port, is not supported.\r\\n<h2>Power System</h2>\r\\nPowering the Phantom fold handset is a Li-Po 5000 mAh, non-removable battery. The 5,000mAh super battery is charged by a 45W flash charger, which powers up 40% in 15 min, and 1-100% in 55 min.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<table id=\"tablepress-3358\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-3358\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-3358-name\">\r\\n<tbody class=\"row-hover\">\r\\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\r\\n<td class=\"column-1\">\r