 feature, either color will fulfil every moment you touch and use your smartphone.\r\\n<h3>A Large, Immersive Display</h3>\r\\nA 6.8-inch screen is a statement of intent by Tecno. It makes the Spark 10 Pro stand out and apart, especially if you love larger screens. The large 6.8-inch IPS LCD has a refresh rate of 90Hz, which is quite decent to keep the screen in peak performance as you browse the internet, chat or consume all of your 30+ min series and latest dram episodes on the device. You will undoubtedly enjoy every minute on the large immersive display with a decent 90Hz refresh rate and 1080 x 2460 pixels (~395 ppi density) resolution.\r\\n<h3>Tecno Spark 10 Pro Best Selfie Camera</h3>\r\\nTecno Spark 10 Pro comes loaded with a 32MP GLOWING Selfie Camera. Shine up your dazzling beauty. Take breathtaking selfies. It is equipped with all-needed glowing selfie technologies to shine you up in any light setting. It comes along with 3 Levels of Adjustable Brightness. Lack the light you need for the perfect selfie? No worries! SPARK 10 Pro sparks it up. The built-in front flashlight offers three adjustable brightness levels to suit different lighting needs.\r\\n\r\\nBright or dark, it invariably captures your highlight moments. 10lux soft light illuminates beauty without glaring in the eyes. The Super flashlight algorithm is also in place to correct any overexposure. So, feel free to shine the way you are! The 32MP ultra-clear front camera teamed up with the 4-in-1 re-mosaic technology – to maximise the light captured by each pixel, thus playing the magic of ultra-clear photography, even in low light. Capture More of the glamour in life, down to the minor details.\r\\n<h3>Tecno Spark 10 Pro Super Main Camera</h3>\r\\nAt the rear, the Spark 10 Pro packs a massive 50MP high-resolution photographic system. Renew your experiences and memories with a 50MP AI Dual-Camera, and psyche yourself up to create a Superstar experience.\r\\n<h4>Super Portraits</h4>\r\\nBrace yourself for Super Portraits captures on your Tecno phone. Reveal the star bit in you. Your style, your call! ASD identifies the portrait and scene, while LUT enhances their colouring and shadowing. For every single shot, colours are fully adapted to skin tones to regenerate the natural colourfulness of your style.\r\\n<h4>Personalized Beautification</h4>\r\\nBreak away from the “one-size-fits-all” beauty. Enhance your glamour from every imaginable dimension to restore the beauty that belongs only to you. The AI on the primary camera learns and keeps your beautification needs in mind, polishing your natural beauty based on gender and a vast series of secret parameters, just like your personal stylist.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Super shots at Night</strong>\r\\n\r\\nMake the nights your own, whether partying with friends or alone enjoying quiet, quality time. Use Black Gold/Green Orange/Ice Blue/Cyberpunk/Romantic/Dreamy Versatile styles of night filters to fit your unique night photography. Break into a world of night fantasies that were never seen before.\r\\n<h4>Vlogging in all scenarios</h4>\r\\nThe camera comes along with rich features to empower video creation. Be the star in your life! Beautify as you move, as you are beautiful in motion.  Focus with the background blurred so that you are always the absolute star. Backlight or dim light, HDR significantly eliminates noises and improves video quality at night.\r\\n<h4>Super Night Algorithm</h4>\r\\nLet out your nocturnal nature with Tecno Spark 10 Pro.  The Super Night Algorithm integrates and aligns multiple frames in 1 shot to find the perfect you and night scene in the dazzles. Grab excellent and awe-inspiring night shots on your Spark 10 Pro, the night superpower!\r\\n<h4>Super Cool for Gamers</h4>\r\\nThe large, 6.8-inch, 1080p IPS display is complemented by a G88 Gaming Processor, making Tecno Spark 10 Pro a darling of gamers. Running on Android 13 OS, you will enjoy upgraded plus new features on Android’s latest platform. HIOS 12.6 enables better UI and customizations to what best defines you.\r\\n\r\\nPowered by Mediatek Helio G88 (12nm) chipset, Spark 10 Pro is a gem for gamers. If you love gaming, you will love the processing power of the phone packs. The chipset has an efficient Octa-core (2×2.0 GHz Cortex-A75 &amp; 6×1.8 GHz Cortex-A55) CPU and Mali-G52 MC2 GPU. Lagging is minimized as you push your handset to the limit while gaming or multi-tasking.\r\\n<h2>Network and Connectivity</h2>\r\\nToo bad Tecno Spark 10 Pro is 4G network-enabled and not 5G. However, the phone still loads and downloads files and data pretty fast. Using Ida Engine 3.0, download via Cellular faster by 45%, Wi-Fi by 300%, and Camp Network by 90%.\r\\n<h3>Assistant</h3>\r\\nTo aid communications, Ella 2.0 is installed on the Spark 10 Pro. Ella 2.0 is a trustworthy, responsive And intelligent assistant that speaks English, French and Nigerian Hausa.\r\\n<h3>Ambient Noise Cancellation</h3>\r\\nYou can filter out background noise. Hear your calls like you are there.\r\\n<h3>AI Album</h3>\r\\nAlgorithm Powered Album that classifies photos, recommends covers, and sorts out your albums.\r\\n<h4>NFC</h4>\r\\nGet things done in a beep without even unlocking your phone.\r\\n<h3>Phone Powering System</h3>\r\\nStay in power for long as you work, chat or play your favourite game. Back in power fast with the 18W fast charger. The 5,000mAh is powerful enough to sustain long hours of gaming or phone calls. When running out of power, plug in the 18W rapid charger, and return to the business in no time.',NULL,NULL,'Tecno-Spark-10-Pro','Tecno-Spark-10-Pro',19500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(233,'Tecno Spark 10 Pro - 128GB','Tecno Spark 10 Pro - 128GB','Tecno-Spark-10-Pro-128GB','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,3,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Tecno Spark 10 Pro - 128GB','Tecno Spark 10 Pro - 128GB',NULL,NULL,'Tecno-Spark-10-Pro-128GB','Tecno-Spark-10-Pro-128GB',24000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(234,'Tecno Spa