ivo’s Funtouch 13 user interface. The Vivo handset is powered by an Octa-core Mediatek MT6765 Helio P35 (12nm) processor and is anchored by 64GB and 4GB RAM. It also comes with a 5MP front camera and 8MP rear primary camera. A 5,000 mAh battery powers the device. The phone comes in Orchid Blue, Cosmic Grey, and Sunset Gold colour variants\r\\n<h3>Design and Built</h3>\r\\nVivo Y02t boasts of a unique, 2.5D trendy design. Combine modern techniques with classic design elements, as a perfect expression of the sense of design and beauty of simplicity. The body is made of a glass display, plastic body and back pane. The thin body looks cool, with the handset measuring 164 x 75.6 x 8.5 mm and weighing 186g. The phone is comfortable to hold and use at Just 8.49 mm thick with a 2.5D slim body and a flat frame.\r\\n\r\\nNotably, Vivo Y02t is Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by), the display screen is resistant to scratches and the matte finish at the back makes it resistant to fingerprints.\r\\n<h3>Display</h3>\r\\nY02t boasts a 6.51-inch FullView&#x2122; Display with HD+ (1600 × 720) resolution, providing a wide immersive view and sharp images. Do not worry about eyestrain because the phone can automatically adjust its screen brightness and filter blue light.\r\\n<h3>Vivo Y02t Camera Setup</h3>\r\\nBe a Master of Photography with Vivo YO2t’s dual camera set up consisting of a single, 8 MP, f/2.0 lens with LED flash and capable of recording 1080p@30fps videos. The selfie camera consists of 5 MP, f/2.2 lens.\r\\n\r\\nWith Face Beauty and Time-Lapse, take as many photos as you want regardless of the environment.\r\\n\r\\nFocus on your beauty with the built-in bokeh algorithm, and make your images more expressive.\r\\n<h3>Performance and Operation on Vivo YO2t</h3>\r\\n<h4>Operating System</h4>\r\\nThe handset runs on Android’s latest 13 operating system + Vivo’s Funtouch 13 OS. Based on Android, Vivo’s Funtouch OS 13 is a highly customized, effective, intelligent, and beautifully designed mobile operating system. The two combine to provide a seamless, smooth and flawless user experience as you navigate through applications and customize and personalize the phone to suit your personality.\r\\n\r\\nFuntouch OS:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Allows easy touch and easy sharing. Phone cloning is easily achieved without the usage of any mobile data.</li>\r\\n 	<li>Face Unlock: Unlock your phone freely whenever necessary.</li>\r\\n 	<li>iManager:the feature clears junk files and checks the security, ensuring your phone is running smoothly all the time.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\n<h4>Processing Unit</h4>\r\\nVivo YO2t possessa decent processing unit. As a 4G smartphone, the octa-core <a href=\"https://i.mediatek.com/p35\">Mediatek MT6765 Helio P35 (12nm)</a> processor provides sufficient processing power for background operations on tasks at hand. Multi-tasking across many open apps will be no trouble for the handset, besides being decent enough to offer good user experience for gaming low to mid-setting gaming. thanks to PowerVR GE8320 GPU, you will have no wasted moments as you immerse yourself in gaming.\r\\n<h4>Memory</h4>\r\\nVivo Y02t (4 GB + 64 GB) features 4 GB of RAM and has a memory trick up its sleeve. Part of your idle ROM space can be used as extended RAM to make switching between apps smoother. Up to 4 GB extended RAM is supported. Feel free to download your favourite apps and run them without lag. The installed 64GB + additional memory (microSDXC (dedicated slot) provides decent capacity for your videos and photo gallery to store and share content as you please.\r\\n<h3>Connectivity and Communication</h3>\r\\nVivo Y02t is 4G enabled. It runs on GSM /  HSPA / LTE network technology, supporting 2G, 3G, 4G bands. Connectivity on 4G is decent and fast enough (HSPA, LTE Network speed), but understandably not as fast and efficient as 5G.\r\\n\r\\nAlternative ways of connectivity include:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>Bluetooth: 5.0, A2DP, LE</li>\r\\n 	<li>Internet: Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band</li>\r\\n 	<li>Radio: FM radio supported</li>\r\\n 	<li>USB: microUSB 2.0, OTG</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nThe handset has loudspeakers for quality audio output, several sensors(Accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass), and positioning (GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, BDS, QZSS). Unfortunately, Vivo Y02t does not support NFC, Infrared data transfer and connectivity with other devices that support these technologies.\r\\n\r\\nBattery and Power Management<strong>\r\\n</strong>Have endless fun with Vivo Y02t. With a 5000 mAh (TYP) large battery, no fear of low battery indication. The battery offers 18 Hours of online HD video streaming before recharge.\r\\n\r\\nOverheating protection ensures charging safety. The 5V/1A reverse charging feature also covers your other electronic devices, which turns your phone into a mobile power bank.',NULL,NULL,'Vivo-Y02t','Vivo-Y02t',18500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(247,'Vivo Y16','Vivo Y16','Vivo-Y16','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,11,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Vivo Y16','<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\">\r\\n<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\">\r\\n<div class=\"mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col entity-sec\">\r\\n<h2>Vivo Y16 Specifications</h2>\r\\n<h4>General</h4>\r\\n<span data-contrast=\"none\">Vivo Y16 is among the most affordable smartphones in the market. If you want to own a 4G smartphone that comes with a good camera system, a long battery life, and an affordable price, then this is a good 4G smartphone in the market.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:330}\"> </span>\r\\n<h3><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">6.51″ inch HD+ Display.</span></b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:330}\"> </span></h3>\r\\n<span data-contrast=\"none\">It has a 6.51″ inch display. The display is a