t design provides a comfortable and smooth grip. Lean into the new minimalism. It measures 164.3 x 76.1 x 8.3 mm and weighs 186g.  the handset is built using a glass front, plastic frame and plastic back. The handset is Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by) and waterproof (IP54, dust and splash resistant).\r\\n\r\\nThe display consists of an IPS LCD 6.56-inch display with a peak brightness of 700 nits (peak) and a refresh rate of 90Hz.  Vivo Y17s boasts a decent high-resolution of 720 x 1612 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~269 ppi density). With such an impressive power display, you are guaranteed an excellent media consumption experience, whether watching videos, playing video games or scanning through your stack of photos. However, 1080p resolution would offer an even better viewing experience.\r\\n<h3>Performance of the Vivo Y17s</h3>\r\\nIt runs on Android 13 OS, with Vivo’s latest Funtouch 13 UI. Use the fast and efficient Octa-core Octa-core (2×2.0 GHz Cortex-A75 &amp; 6×1.8 GHz Cortex-A55) CPU, Mali-G52 MC2 GPU. They enable easy use of the device, multi-tasking, playing videos and browsing the internet. A <a href=\"https://www.mediatek.com/products/smartphones-2/mediatek-helio-g85\">Mediatek MT6769 Helio G85</a> chipset uses 12nm processing technology for improved performance and lower power consumption, which certainly improves the overall performance of the Vivo Y17s.\r\\n\r\\nFor optimal performance, the device comes equipped with massive internal space. Vivo created only one variant for the Vivo Y17s brand: 128GB 6GB RAM. This is quite commendable, considering such RAM guarantees fast processing and the 128GB is sufficient for storing large files (pictures, videos and documents). Besides, the device comes with a dedicated MicroSD slot.\r\\n<h3>Vivo Y17s Camera Set-up</h3>\r\\nThe camera setup is a prominent stand-out feature you must note. Take awesome, professional-looking selfies and videos on your device. Vivo installed a decent 8 MP, f/2.0, (wide) front camera on their Y17s handset, capable of taking 1080p@30fps videos.\r\\n\r\\nThe handset is equipped with a Dual 50 MP, f/1.8, (wide), PDAF + 2 MP, f/2.4, (depth) lens at the back. It features an LED flash and is capable of 1080p@30fps video capture.\r\\n\r\\nThe Portrait Light Effect creates distinctive selfies with a variety of light effects. You’ll see yourself in a new light!\r\\n\r\\nPortrait Bokeh Aura Screen Light makes your portrait brighter and more transparent with natural-looking bokeh, ensuring you’re the focal point that turns heads.\r\\n\r\\nBokeh Flare Portrait helps capture stunning portrait shots that naturally highlight the subject and create beautiful bokeh flare effects with our rear portrait algorithm.\r\\n<h3>Connectivity on Vivo Y17s</h3>\r\\nVivo Y17s is a 4G-enabled device. It supports up to 4G bands, with up to HSPA, LTE speeds. Enjoy decent uploading and downloading speed for videos and other media forms, though it would be faster on 5G.\r\\n\r\\nTo connect with other devices, use WI-FI (Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band), Bluetooth (5.0, A2DP, LE), USB Type-C 2.0, and USB On-The-Go.\r\\n\r\\nA GPS (A-GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, BDS, QZSS) is installed on the device for better motoring navigability. Sensors on the device include a fingerprint (side-mounted), accelerometer, proximity, gyro, and compass.\r\\n<h3>Battery</h3>\r\\nPowering the device is a powerful and reliable 5,000mAh Li-Po non-removable battery. A fast, fast-charging 15W wired adapter comes with the device to give you that fast charging option.',NULL,NULL,'Vivo-Y17s','Vivo-Y17s',21000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(249,'Vivo Y27s','Vivo Y27s','Vivo-Y27s','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,11,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Vivo Y27s','<h2><strong>Vivo Y27s Specifications in Kenya</strong></h2>\r\\nVivo Y27s price in Kenya is Ksh 32,000. The device, released on November 07, 2023, has a 6.64-inch IPS LCD, 120Hz display with a 1080 x 2388 pixels screen resolution. It is powered by an Octa-core Qualcomm SM6225 Snapdragon 680 4G (6 nm) processor that comes along with an Adreno 610 GPU. The phone has 128GB, 8GB RAM / 256GB, and 8GB RAM internal storage, and runs on Android 13 with Funtouch 13 UI, powered by a 5,000 mAh battery with 44W fast charging. The phone packs a dual rear camera setup consisting of a 50 MP (wide) primary sensor, a 2MP (depth) sensor, and an 8 MP, f/2.0 (wide) selfie camera.\r\\n<h3>Product Description</h3>\r\\n<h4>Physical Attributes</h4>\r\\nVivo Y27s is a 4G-Network enabled phone that makes people say wow upon viewing it and holding it up in their palms. The vibrant dual-ring design provides twice the coolness impression compared to other phones. Whether you are detail-oriented or more of a first-impression person, prepare to be amazed by the simple yet straightforward outlines and excellent ring-shaped design.\r\\n\r\\nThe phone measures 164.1 x 76.2 x 8.2 mm (6.46 x 3.00 x 0.32 in) and weighs 192g (slightly heavier and thicker when compared to Vivo Y27). Notably, the phone is slim, light, and simply a pleasure to look at, thanks to the flat frame that is also ultra-thin and super light. It is made of:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>A Glass front;</li>\r\\n 	<li>plastic frame,</li>\r\\n 	<li>a plastic back.</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nIt comes in Burgundy Black and Garden Green colors.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Burgundy Colour</strong>: Luxurious red meets deep black in Burgundy Black. It combines shimmering shades from Glitter AG’s matte surface to experience premium elegance in your hand.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Garden Green:</strong> Get closer to nature. The neat green color, featuring a yellow hue and combined with shimmering, sparkling textures, brings refreshing, joyful vibes.\r\\n\r\\nYour Vivo phone is an extension of yourself.  With all these trendy colors and a scratch-resistant, sparkling crystalline matte finish, you will find something that matches your style and popularity.\r\\n<h4>Display</h4>\r\\nThe FHD+ Sunlight display with 600 nits peak brightness undoubtedly fits the stylish design and high expectations that come along with such a fantastic phone perfectly.\r\\n\r\\nNot only is the 6.64 IPS LCD with 1080 x 2388 pixels (~395 ppi density) resolution display immersive, but it is also great for indoor and outdoor use. You can use it comfortably outdoors as you would use it indoors, as it offers both clarity and pleasure. Moreover, the FHD+ Sunlight display ensures that everything you see is clear, even if you are bathed in sunlight.\r\\n<h4>Waterproof Rating</h4>\r\\nThe phone is IP54-rated. Pollution, hazy weather, and water splashes will always happen. However, it would be best not to worry about such incidences since you are now protected.\r\\n<h4>Cameras</h4>\r\\nThe decent front and rear camera set-up lets you capture the wow moment. Every shot counts.\r\\n<h5>Selfie Shots</h5>\r\\nTake awesome selfies on the 8 MP, f/2.0, (wide) camera that equally records videos at 1080p@30fps. With the 8MP HD front camera, capture amazing selfies in high definition with accurate focus, revealing your best look.\r\\n\r\\nActively engage in taking nightly selfies, too. What is darkness?  The Night Portrait and Aura Screen Light allow you or your subjects to shine at all times, notwithstanding the illuminating of the hour.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>AI Face Beauty:</strong> The feature provides more options for beauty than usual.  You will instantly\r\\n\r\\nHave a naturally excellent skin tone without any beauty naps.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Bokeh Flare Portrait:</strong> Take shots with captivating feels. Messy lights and a messed-up background should be fine for you. With the background lights blurred, your subject will stand out and create a heart-melting vibe.\r\\n<h5>Main Camera</h5>\r\\nIt comprises a 50 MP, f/1.8, (wide) PDAF camera, complemented by a 2 MP, f/2.4 (depth) sensor.\r\\n\r\\nThe 50MP primary camera lets you capture ultra-sharp details of objects in focus. The camera has everything, from stunning details to dazzling night shots.\r\\n\r\\nThe 2MP Bokeh Camera also creates a cinematic-grade bokeh effect, allowing your subject to stand out wonderfully.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Movie Making:</strong> With the Cinematic Aspect Ratio, everyone can capture cinematic videos that are fit for the big screen now.\r\\n<h4>Performance of the VIVO Y27s</h4>\r\\n<h5>Operating System</h5>\r\\nThe phone runs on Android’s latest OS, 13, with upgrades as they come over the years. For customization and a better User Interface, use the Funtouch 13.\r\\n<h5>Processing Unit</h5>\r\\nIt loads raw processing power with an impressive and powerful <a href=\"https://www.qualcomm.com/products/mobile/snapdragon/smartphones/snapdragon-6-series-mobile-platforms/snapdragon-680-4g-mobile-platform\">Qualcomm SM6225 Snapdragon 680 4G (6 nm)</a> chipset that comes along with a reliable Octa-core (4×2.4 GHz Kryo 265 Gold &amp; 4×1.9 GHz Kryo 265 Silver) CPU and Adreno 610 GPU. The processing unit works in unison to give uncompromised experiences as you multi-task between applications and maximize your gaming and video entertainment. Thanks to its intricate, high-performance processing unit and related features, there are no lags, overheating, or annoying buffering experiences when surfing the internet with the Vivo Y27s.\r\\n<h5>Memory</h5>\r\\nThe device has 128GB/256GB internal memory and 8GB RAM. The memory booster on the Vivo Y27s makes it a high-performance handset based on its specifications and capabilities. Besides, an extended RAM 3.0 means extended smoothness.  Assuredly, you can run and switch between multiple apps smoothly (up to 25) with the new generation ample RAM 3.0 that supports up to 8GB of extended RAM.\r\\n\r\\nYou are in safe hands with the RAM saver.  Whatever you are up to, whatever tasks you have, enjoy boosted memory for more space and smoother and quicker app switching.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>No lagging: </strong>You should not, as anyone ought not to lag when switching apps. The Interface Preserver feature precisely cuts reloading out, so you are always up to speed.\r\\n<h5>Security</h5>\r\\nFor any smartphone, security is usually a top concern for users. For Vivo Y27s, you can keep secrets to yourself. With screen pinning, you can access only what you allow.\r\\n<h5>Durability and Versatility</h5>\r\\nWhether scratched, dropped, or exposed to weather conditions, the Vivo Y27s will still perform and remain in top condition. It is a durable, reliable phone, perfect for the occasional or frequent case of butter fingers.\r\\n<h5>Tailor-made for you</h5>\r\\n<strong>Gaming Mode</strong>: Get higher running and loading speeds on your Vivo phone for your selected games, video, and everything that falls in between regarding work and fun.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Faster Widget Access:</strong> Smaller widgets give you faster, quicker, and easier access. It means less waiting and getting worked up.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>iManager that settles everything:</strong> The iManager enables you to monitor app usage time and prevent overheating, among other functions, allowing optimal phone functioning.\r\\n\r\\n<strong>Make your Phone Uncopiable:</strong> Personalize your system and app colours. Through customizations, thanks to Funtouch 13, your Vivo Y27 would not be able to look like someone else’s as you project and express your personality.\r\\n<h4>Connectivity on Vivo Y27s</h4>\r\\n<h5>Network</h5>\r\\nThe phone is 4G enabled, supporting 2G, 3G, and 4G Network bands. Notably, the uploading and downloading speeds for files and apps are decent enough (HSPA, LTE) to complete work with considerable time.\r\\n<h5><strong>NFC</strong></h5>\r\\nYou can now live with NFC. Payments and top-ups can now be made entirely through your phone and nothing else, lessening your time and trouble in finding alternative ways to make transactions.\r\\n<h5><strong>Internet</strong></h5>\r\\nConnect seamlessly and without much hustle with the installed Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac and dual-band WLAN on the phone. Connectivity is now in record time, more secure and stable than even poor networks, thus enabling smooth connectivity and less interference, especially when streaming, downloading, uploading files, or streaming games.\r\\n<h5><strong>USB</strong></h5>\r\\nUse the USB Type-C 2.0 OTG for fast data transfer to your USB stick or other devices. The port is equally handy for recharging the device.\r\\n<h4>Battery and Power Management</h4>\r\\nThe Li-Po 5,000 mAh, non-removable battery does a splendid job in powering systems and the display of the Vivo Y27s. Whether it is all work or all-day play, the battery raised to the occasion with a splendid performance. It provides:\r\\n<ul>\r\\n 	<li>81 Hours Standby</li>\r\\n 	<li>63 Hours of Video Streaming</li>\r\\n 	<li>89 Hours of Mobile Gaming</li>\r\\n</ul>\r\\nThe power capacity is enough to do everything you need.  It even protects you with its 24-dimension Security Protection feature.\r\\n\r\\nYou can instantly recharge your phone with the 44W FlashCharge unit that comes with the phone. It charges the battery quickly, up to 30% in 15 minutes. As such, you can make the best of the short bursts of recharging to get back online or back to make those long, vital calls.\r\\n\r\\nThe charging system allows reverse wired charging, making it possible to recharge your smart devices such as BT headset, smartwatch, and earbuds on the go without needing to plug in directly into a power source.',NULL,NULL,'Vivo-Y27s','Vivo-Y27s',33000,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(250,'Vivo Y35','Vivo Y35','Vivo-Y35','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,11,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Vivo Y35','<h2>Vivo Y35</h2>\r\\nVivo Y35 runs on the Qualcomm SM6225 Snapdragon 680 4G (6 nm) processor with Adreno 610 GPU. The Vivo Y35 has 8 GB RAM and 256 GB of internal storage which is expandable using microSDXC (dedicated slot). The phone has a 6.58 inches, 1080 x 2408 pixels IPS display with a pixel density of 401 ppi. Coming to cameras, it has a 50 MP rear camera and a 16 MP front camera for selfies.\r\\n\r\\nThere is a fingerprint sensor present on the Vivo Y35 as well, along with a magnetic field sensor (compass), gyroscope sensor, proximity sensor, and accelerometer sensor. It is a dual SIM smartphone with support for 3G, USB OTG, Wi-Fi, FM Radio, and GPS too. It has a USB Type-C port for data syncing and charging. The Vivo Y35 runs on Android 11 and all this is powered by a 5000 mAh battery. It measures 164.3 x 76.1 x 8.3 mm (height x width x thickness) with a total weight of 188 grams including the battery.\r\\n\r\\n&nbsp;\r\\n<h3>Build and Display</h3>\r\\nVivo Y35 is a big and elegant-looking device. It measures 164.3 x 76.1 x 8.3 mm and weighs 188g.  the handset is built using a front glass front, plastic frame, and plastic back. The display consists of an IPS LCD 6.58-inch display, with a peak brightness of 550 HBM and a refresh rate of 90Hz.  The phone boasts of an impressively high resolution of 1080 x 2408 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~401 ppi density). With such an impressive power display, you guaranteed of awesome media consumption experience whether you are watching videos, playing video games or scanning through your stack of photos.\r\\n<h3>Performance</h3>\r\\nIt runs on Android 11, <a href=\"https://www.91mobiles.com/hub/funtouch-os-12-update-tracker-supported-devices/\">Funtouch 12 OS</a>. Make use of the fast and powerful Octa-core (4×2.4 GHz Kryo 265 Gold &amp; 4×1.9 GHz Kryo 265 Silver) CPU, Adreno 610 GPU. They enable easy use of the device, be multi-tasking, playing videos and browsing on the internet. A Qualcomm SM6225 Snapdragon 680 4G (6 nm) chipset makes use of 6nm Process Technology for improved performance and lower power consumption, which certainly improves the overall performance of the Vivo Y35.\r\\n\r\\nFor optimal performance, the device comes equipped with massive internal space. Vivo created 3 variants for the Vivo Y35 brand: 64GB 4GB RAM, 128GB 8GB RAM, 256GB 8GB RAM. Make your choice best on your budget and usage. Besides, the device comes along with a dedicated MicroSD slot. Powering the device is a powerful and reliable 5,000mAh, Li-Po nonremovable battery. Fast charging 44W wired adapter comes with the device to give you that fast charging option.\r\\n<h3>Camera</h3>\r\\nOther than a robust performance on the Vivo Y35, the camera setup is a major stand-out feature you must take note. Take awesome, professional-looking selfies and videos on your device. Vivo installed a massive 16 MP, f/2.0, (wide) front camera on their Y35 handset, capable of taking 1080p@30fps videos.\r\\n\r\\nAt the back, the handset is equipped with a triple 50 MP, f/1.8, (wide), PDAF + 2 MP, f/2.4, (macro) + 2 MP, f/2.4, (depth) lenses. It features LED flash and is capable of 1080p@30fps video capture.\r\\n<h3>Connectivity</h3>\r\\nVivo Y35 is a 4G-enabled device. It supports up to 4G bands, with up to HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE speed. To connect with other devices, use WI-FI, Bluetooth, and USB Type-C 2.0, USB On-The-Go. Installed on the device is a GPS (A-GPS, GLONASS, GALILEO, BDS, QZSS) for better navigability when motoring. Sensors on the device are a fingerprint (side-mounted), accelerometer, proximity, gyro, and compass.',NULL,NULL,'Vivo-Y35','Vivo-Y35',29500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(251,'Xiaomi 12','Xiaomi 12','Xiaomi-12','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,5,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Xiaomi 12','<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\"><h2>Xiaomi 12 in Kenya</h2><p>The Xiaomi 12 price in Kenya is around KSh 85',NULL,NULL,'Xiaomi-12','Xiaomi-12',89999,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(252,'Xiaomi 12 Pro','Xiaomi 12 Pro','Xiaomi-12-Pro','uploads/custom-images/img.png',0,5,0,0,0,20,'200',0,'Xiaomi 12 Pro','<div class=\"electro-description clearfix\"><h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Xiaomi 12 Pro in Kenya</span></h2><p>The Xiaomi 12 Pro price in Kenya is around KSh 98',NULL,NULL,'Xiaomi-12-Pro','Xiaomi-12-Pro',95500,NULL,NULL,0,1,1,1,1,1,1,0,1,NULL,NULL),(253